<p><span><strong>网友：就看到了“全是肉”</strong><strong></strong></span></p>
<p><strong><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200811/e74fe6238892456ab2613e1ae1e05c2d.png" /></strong></p>
